<div class="title">Warm Rushes Throughout The Body</div>
<div class="substance">Alprazolam & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=IowaPunker&Exact=1">IowaPunker</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; IowaPunker. "Warm Rushes Throughout The Body: An Experience with Alprazolam & Alcohol (exp14564)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. May 23, 2002. erowid.org/exp/14564</div>

<br/>



